: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>Describe the performance of the fund relative to its benchmark during the last three months.</strong></p> <p>Equity markets registered solid gains for the quarter as the long-awaited interest-rate cut by the US Federal Reserve (Fed) arrived. The Bank of England (BOE) and the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1360003423/image_1360003423.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742339-bny-mellon-equity-income-fund-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 17:59:00"}, {"id": "4742336", "title": "Berkshire Hathaway Should Be Broken Up", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/506794609/image_506794609.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"BNSF Train, Burlington Northern Santa Fe\" data-id=\"506794609\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5580px\" height=\"3720px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/506794609/image_506794609.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/506794609/image_506794609.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/506794609/image_506794609.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/506794609/image_506794609.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/506794609/image_506794609.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/506794609/image_506794609.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/506794609/image_506794609.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s